data.description: Exclusive Agency Listing. All agents may advertise this property with exceptions of MLS and yard signs. HUD homes are sold "as is". HUD Case #495-874875. Welcome to this remarkable and rare opportunity nestled within the highly desirable Northwood neighborhood, renowned for its tree-lined streets, lush landscapes, and easy access to premier schools, shopping, dining, and recreational facilities. This spacious 5 bedroom, 3.1 bath home has 3 living areas, a 2 car garage, and sits on an expansive corner lot spanning 0.819 acres.  This is truly a blank canvas with endless possibilities, awaiting your creative vision to transform it into your dream home! No representation is made to information provided including taxes, sqft, schools, features, etc. Buyer must verify all information.
